Package: surveySoFR
Type: Package
Title: surveySoFR: A package for estimation and inference of scalar on function regression models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrew Leroux, Erjia Cui, Lucia Tabacu, Ekaterina Smirnova
Maintainer: Andrew Leroux <andrew.leroux@cuanschutz.edu>
Description: This package facilitates estimation and inference for scalar on function regression using penalized regression splines. Estimation is performed using the mgcv package. The primary functionality of this package is contained in the function doBRR() which implements balanced repeated resampling for estimating regression coefficients. 
